title: slapd syncrepl status
agents: linux
catalog: app/slapd
license: GPL
distribution: Markus Weber
description:
 This check monitors the status of the syncreplication of a slapd consumer.
 From version 1.1 it can also monitor Multi-Master replication.

item:
 SLAPD <Instance name> syncrepl status

[parameters]
parameters (dict):

perfdata:
 Deltatime

inventory:
 One service will be created for each slapd instance configured in lokal config file.
